I loved this series! The fifth year seemed to stretch the 'over the top' limit a little, but was still good as well. My personal favorites were the first season (The Murder House) and the third season (The Asylum) although they were all very good. I particularly found the screen plays and the writing outstanding! I was amazed at how they seemed to almost use the actors as a troupe and I loved seeing the actors in different character personas in the different seasons. Just outstanding! Well worth a watch!
